{# Template for ParseToolInput - parses natural language to tool input #}
{% macro tool_input_wrapper(tool_name, tool_description, input_schema, task, context, examples) %}
Tool {
    Name: {{ tool_name }}
    Description: {{ tool_description }}
    Input Schema: {{ input_schema }}
}
Task: {{ task }}
Context: {{ context }}
Return a json in the following format to call the tool to solve the task or return a json with the error message if you cannot call the tool and solve the task:
Example Responses: {
{%- for example in examples %}
    Response: {{ example }}
{%- endfor %}
}
Response:
{% endmacro %}
